text: Jo Seong-min (born 5 January 1976) is a South Korean gymnast. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Gymnasts at the 1998 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 1998 Asian Games
